window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Serendipity Collection is a series of love triangles featuring different couples in books 1 to 4 and a full epilogue in book 5.</p> <p>INTOXICATION:<br> Billionaire Romance<br> Sianna is about to celebrate Christmas with her boyfriend's family until she meets his father, her hot one night stand from two years ago. Discover how this drama unfolds with broken hearts and all the angst.</p> <p>INCOGNITO:<br> Single Dad Romance<br> Coming out of a seven year coma, Ashrika married her savior until she meets another man who'll do anything to make her his despite her marital status. Find out who she chooses in this tension-filled drama.</p> <p>INFALLIBLE:<br> Mafia Romance<br> What happens when a Capo falls in love, in a relationship that was never meant to be. Will he win or does fate need to play a hand?</p> <p>INDESTRUCTIBLE:<br> Mafia Romance<br> When Gianna is sold to a powerful Don to pay off her father's debt, what he doesn't expect is to encounter a married young woman. Uncover her growth, her defiance and maneuvering the love of two men.</p> <p>INEVITABLE:<br> The Epilogue<br> Discover life after their respective HEA's for all our couples.</p> <p><b>PLEASE NOTE: When you purchase this title, the accompanying PDF will be available in your Audible Library along with the audio.</b></p>"; 
